WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.420
This technological shift creates tension between business outcomes and human

00:00:04.420 --> 00:00:08.840
outcomes. You must navigate this through Stagility: the calculated balance

00:00:08.840 --> 00:00:13.260
of systemic disruption and cultural stability. You must provide stable

00:00:13.260 --> 00:00:17.680
anchors so your people feel safe enough to innovate rapidly.

00:00:17.680 --> 00:00:22.100
This requires radical employee centricity and empathy, applying cognitive empathy,

00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:26.520
emotional empathy, and empathic concern to eliminate low-value work.
